{"tid":2249594,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"唔買 Apple 原廠 MagSafe 充電板   無線充電攻率即時減半","createTime":"2020-10-19T12:25:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T18:05:27.000Z","uid":58335,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"9bcbe68e567477f3743a5e8b0b002334b554ef10","tid":2249594,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T12:25:54.000Z","msg":"全新 iPhone 12 系列悉數支援 MagSafe 無線充電技術，簡單來說就是在現有的無線充電之上，加入磁吸式功能，讓手機能夠對準無線充電板和避免充電期間移位。Apple 在發佈會上表示 MagSafe 支援 Qi 無線充電標準，但並沒有在席間透露細節。<br />\n<img src=\"https://timgm.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2020-10/16/216944/eprice_1_a0342cca48e66a76b191fb557d68d687.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgm.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2020-10%2F16%2F216944%2Feprice_1_a0342cca48e66a76b191fb557d68d687.jpg&h=5d5c6732&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nApple 標榜以 MagSafe 充電器為 iPhone 12 系列無線充電，功率最高為 15W；雖然 Apple 表示 iPhone 12 用戶可以使用任何 Qi 標準的無線充電板，但原來這些非 MagSafe 充電規格的產品，其最高功率只得 7.5W。換句話說，假如 iPhone 12 用戶希望獲得最快的無線充電速度，只有選購 Apple 原廠 MagSafe 無線充電器，或等待未來第三方廠商推出 MagSafe 規格的無線充電裝置。<br />\n<br />\n另一值得留意的細節是，MagSafe 無線充電器能夠用於所有支援無線充電的 iPhone，不過 15W 快速充電只對應最新的 iPhone 12 系列。<br />\n <br />\n資料來源：macrumors<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4544/216944/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4544%2F216944%2F1%2F&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZpNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=a4ab29ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4544/216944/1/</a>"},{"pid":"53718d3a6aa37b9d51276894cf0e5323b60dd3dd","tid":2249594,"uid":344625,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T12:27:27.000Z","msg":"攻率<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30f60a86b7810b6fabef86ed38c9bb391f1f32b","tid":2249594,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T12:28:11.000Z","msg":"<im