www.logitech.com/en-us/products/chargers/powered-wireless-charging-3-in-1-dock.950-000015.html?crid=1894\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.logitech.com%2Fen-us%2Fproducts%2Fchargers%2Fpowered-wireless-charging-3-in-1-dock.950-000015.html%3Fcrid%3D1894&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZpNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=999a8d65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.logitech.com/en-us/products/chargers/powered-wireless-charging-3-in-1-dock.950-000015.html?crid=1894</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個我都有買平靚正鍾意佢可以打橫放喺度 睇嘢keep 住無線充電<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.logitech.com/zh-hk/product/powered-iphone-wireless-charging?crid=1537\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.logitech.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fproduct%2Fpowered-iphone-wireless-charging%3Fcrid%3D1537&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZpNY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=128e89b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.logitech.com/zh-hk/product/powered-iphone-wireless-charging?crid=1537</a>"},{"pid":"782cfcf32aa5dd797160c45caa804ae11583a979","tid":2249594,"uid":21378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T03:30:32.000Z","msg":"放心 一定比人破解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 強國咁多人材。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa1d413f9279581936fe2232732ef8930a43eae","tid":2249594,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T03:39:40.000Z","msg":"即係第三廠要出一個同一標準又要交陀地費？咁第三廠咪永遠貴過佢？好似係反競爭行為嚟"},{"pid":"51e2a7866353b62d69bd5f0bc8e10dd51f52f412","tid":2249594,"uid":6777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T03:44:37.000Z","msg":"個標題好奇怪<br />\n<br />\n究竟係因為市面最大功率得7.5w<br />\n定iphone 唔用magesafe 就限制功率係7.5w?<br />\n<br />\n講到好似係apple 既錯咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b92db2d121119cb0b63a36075156be2cc537ab96","tid":2249594,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53718d3a6aa37b9d51276894cf0e5323b60dd3dd","tid":2249594,"